<extension id="restricted_entries" status="experimental" xmlns="http://symphony-cms.com/schemas/extension/1.0">
	<name>Restricted Entries</name>
	<description>
		Restricts authors to selected entries only.
		This extensions offers real security, as any attempt to view or edit un-allowed entries
		in will result in a security exception.
		This exception is also written in Symphony's log.

